      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. The chassis maintains excellent torsional rigidity, paired with a variable M differential lock for precise torque distribution. Essential preventative maintenance has been completed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure the integrity of the high-revving valvetrain and rear suspension geometry. While displaying minor aesthetic character consistent with its age, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain exceptionally sharp for the discerning enthusiast.",
